You can get there.

00:58:05.939 --> 00:58:06.939
Absolutely.

00:58:06.939 --> 00:58:07.939
Believe in yourself.

00:58:07.939 --> 00:58:09.939
Yeah, we all have questions.

00:58:09.939 --> 00:58:10.939
We all have questions.

00:58:10.939 --> 00:58:15.939
I mean, it's really about how you deal with who can help you.

00:58:15.939 --> 00:58:16.939
Find a mentor.

00:58:16.939 --> 00:58:18.939
That's really the one thing.

00:58:18.939 --> 00:58:21.939
People can actually take you by the hand where you are at the moment

00:58:21.939 --> 00:58:23.939
and then pay back to the community.

00:58:23.939 --> 00:58:27.939
So that is literally my number one is, like, don't doubt yourself.

00:58:27.939 --> 00:58:29.939
If you don't know, ask somebody.

00:58:29.939 --> 00:58:31.939
Get some help and pay back.

00:58:31.939 --> 00:58:33.939
You know, give interns, if you have a chance,

00:58:33.939 --> 00:58:35.939
give interns a chance to work in your organization.

00:58:35.939 --> 00:58:38.939
Take a data intern, a data scientist intern, somebody,

00:58:39.939 --> 00:58:41.939
give them a chance to work on real problems.

